 Afro-soul singer/songwriter, Elmina on Tuesday, December 8, 2020 hosted fans and friends to an evening of soul-stirring music at the listening party for her new single titled, ‘Hold On Me’.  Managed by Tokindrumz Management, the glamorous event took place at TOC Hotel, Lekki, Lagos, and marked the beginning of promotion for her upcoming 2021 Afro-EP.  At the occasion were notable personalities of the media and entertainment industry.  